messages.text: Hey, is this Maddy?
No, I’m sorry, who is this?
This is Jay.
I’m the guy who’s number you gave to after we hooked up last night at Mike’s party.
Remember?
Oh, Jay. Yeah, I’m so sorry but this isn’t Maddy’s number.
I’m Miranda. I go to college with Maddy though.
I think she may have given you the wrong number.
Oh are you serious?
Damn. I’m sorry Miranda.
It’s all good.
It’s not like this is the first time this has happened to me before haha.
Really haha?
How many times have you had random guys text you in the middle of a Sunday?
More than I’ve wanted to haha.
Haha jeez, I’m sorry.
Eh, it’s all good.
Most guys immediately send dick pics thinking it’s the girl they hooked up with.
So at least you were smart enough not to do that ;)
HAHAHA oh my god.
I don’t understand what guys are thinking when they send those.
Believe you me, I don’t either.
You’re like one of the few guys that I’ve actually responded to.
Well, that’s not such a high bar to climb I guess all things considered haha.
It is to me at least.
So, Miranda, since I was going to ask Maddy this, I’ll just ask you.
How has your Sunday been going so far?
It’s been fine. I’ve just been studying for a mid term this week.
Organic chemistry is going to be the end of me lol.
Wait, so, you said you go to the same college as Maddy right?
Yeah, FDU. Why?
Because I go to FDU too.
I’m in the same lecture as Maddy in her organic chemistry class on Tuesdays.
Small world, so am I.
We’ve probably seen each other passing papers around or something.
Probably.
So are you cramming before the mid term like me then?
Well obviously not if you’re texting me haha.
Honestly, organic chemistry is a really easy subject for me.
Science has always come pretty easy to me.
Well, that’s good at least I’ll know who to sit next to on Tuesday ;)
Hahaha if you want to, I guess.
The real problem for me has always been history.
I can’t remember dates or places or events to save my life haha.
Really? I’m such a history nerd it’s sort of pathetic haha.
I’m actually studying to be an anthropologist with a minor in archeology if you can believe that.
Wow, that’s actually really cool. I don’t know anyone else studying that.
Yeah, well, outside of Jurassic Park, you don’t see too many archeologists or anthropologists.
It’s not a very sexy profession.
I can’t even think of seeing any in pop culture outside of Jurassic Park to be honest.
Exactly my point haha!
Still really cool that’s what you want to do though, going against the grain.
I have a lot of friends who want to be accountants or art teachers, something like that.
A lot of the same old, same old, you know?
And two very different sides of the pay scale spectrum haha.
Definitely. I mean, those art teachers get paid all the big bucks these days haha.
Hahaha you’re pretty funny, you know that?
Thanks. So are you.
Honestly, you’re the best guy I’ve talked to because of these random texts.
No joke.
Well, you’re the best girl I’ve ever accidentally talked to because I got a wrong number haha.
Also the only one to be fair so there’s not a huge sample size.
So there’s obviously plenty more girls for you to get wrong numbers from in order to get more data for a better sample size then naturally.
Naturally. It’s just proper science that way haha.
Of course.
But yeah, so, once I was gonna ask Maddy this but, hey, what the hell?
You wanna get a cup of coffee or something to eat maybe, like, after midterms are over?
Sure, yeah. Sounds good to me.
And Jay?
Yeah, Miranda?
You can call me Maddy btw from now on.
You passed.
Wait, what?
I’m sorry. What are you talking about?
You passed my test, Jay.
Your test? So this isn’t Miranda I’m talking to?
This is Maddy?
Yeah, it’s Maddy. I’m sorry for lying to you.
I just wanted to make sure of something.
What the hell?
What did you want to make sure of by lying to me?
Look, I’m sorry for lying to you.
I just wanted to make sure you weren’t gonna be a prick after last night, you know?
I’ve had bad luck with guys after hook ups lately.
I mean, I told you about the dick pics right haha?
Yeah, you certainly did lol.
Well, I’m sorry that’s happened to you Maddy but I mean, you didn’t need to lie to me, you know?
I know, I know. I’m an asshole.
I just didn’t want to get hurt again, I guess.
If you don’t want to get coffee after mid terms, I understand.
Look, I’m not saying I don’t want to but was all that real?
The archeology, the wittiness, is that the real Maddy I talked to?
Or was it just Miranda?
Yeah, that’s me. It’s not just Miranda.
I promise.
Well, regardless of who I talked to, Miranda, Maddy, whoever, that’s who I want to go on a date with.
I wonder who’s going to show up.
It’ll be Maddy. Don’t worry.
Alright, well, I’m glad. I had a good conversation with Miranda.
I’m looking forward to an even better one with Maddy. :)
Right back at ya, Jay.
